<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Chaplain" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Chaplain,</orth> an ecclesiastic who performs service in a chapel: <cit><quote>the c. of the Tower,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 4.3.29" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 3, 29</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. h8 5.3.16" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 V, 3, 16</bibl>. Also one that officiates in domestic worship: <bibl n="shak. 3h6 1.3.3" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C I, 3, 3</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 1.2.162" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 I, 2, 162</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 1.2.162" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 I, 2, 162</bibl>
